{
  "texts": [
    "In addition, 15% of the surveyed educators mentioned using ChatGPT to \"write academic and research papers.\"",
    "Eleven percent use ChatGPT to generate feedback on student outputs such as, \"when detecting the similarity index of written papers,\" and \"when checking the grammar, style, and mechanics of my students' essays.\"",
    "Nine percent (9%) indicated other uses of ChatGPT beyond the options we listed.",
    "They use ChatGPT (1) to generate business correspondence, (2) to get suggested titles for created works, (3) to refine all types of written works, and (4) to have fun.",
    "Please see Fig. 9."
  ]
}